snippet.title: AEW: Fight Forever | The Storm Is Coming Trailer
snippet.description:
The Champ is here! AEW Women's World Champion Toni Storm joins the AEW: Fight Forever roster! Turn up the volume on the new premium music tracks, personalize your wrestlers with new customization options & flex on your opponents in the ring!

The Storm is Coming DLC is available on consoles & PC today! ⛈️ 

The Storm is Coming DLC is part of the Season Pass 2 which includes: 3 more talents added to the roster, 37 brand-new move-sets, 60 new attire parts for your wrestler, the Dynamite arena, and a new single-player mode.
